## Truth vs wish

Do **not** claim to have run "in Opus" while shipping subagent output. If
this rule was violated in the same session, **say so** in the PR body and
the Slack reply, with the timestamp and a one-line corrective action — the
operator considers undeclared model swaps a serious trust break.
